snippet.title: Caprisious - The adventures of C-137
snippet.description:
This game was made during 5 days at Castle Game Jam in Örebro 2018. The team consisted of four members:

Robert Esbjörnsson: Code, Design and Team Lead
Mårten Jonsson: Sound and music
Fabian Golz: Artist
Johan Ström: Code

The game is available for free download here: 
https://yrgo-game-programmer.itch.io/c137
